Pre-Game Insights: Egypt booked their spot in the round-of-16 as runners-up in Group B
Congo DR qualified as runners-up in Group F
This will be the ninth meeting between the two sides, with Egypt winning six and drawing two
Miscellaneous Highlights: Each of Egypt's last six internationals have featured goals in both halves, with all three at this AFCON seeing exactly three goals scored in the second half
Congo DR have won just one of their last 10 internationals (six draws)
Others: The winner of this tie will face either Equatorial Guinea or Guinea in the quarterfinal
